#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStorageIntegration.php:95
msgid "Step 2: Create Storage Zone"
msgstr "步驟 2：建立 Storage Zone"

#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStorageIntegration.php:96
msgid "In your BunnyCDN dashboard, navigate to Storage and create a new Storage Zone. This will be used to store your video files."
