#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStorageIntegration.php:98
msgid "Choose a region closest to your audience for better performance."
msgstr "請選擇最靠近您受眾的地區，以獲得更佳效能。"

#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStorageIntegration.php:101
msgid "Step 3: Get Storage Credentials"
msgstr "步驟 3：取得 Storage 憑證"

#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStorageIntegration.php:102
msgid "After creating the storage zone, you'll get the FTP/Storage credentials including username and password."
msgstr "建立 Storage Zone 後，您將取得包含使用者名稱與密碼的 FTP/Storage 憑證。"

#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStorageIntegration.php:104
msgid "These credentials are different from your account login credentials."
msgstr "這些憑證與您的帳號登入憑證不同。"

#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStorageIntegration.php:107
msgid "Step 4: Note the Hostname"
msgstr "步驟 4：記下 Hostname"

#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStorageIntegration.php:108
msgid "The storage hostname is typically \"storage.bunnycdn.com\" but may vary based on your region."
msgstr "Storage hostname 通常為「storage.bunnycdn.com」，但可能依地區有所不同。"

#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStorageIntegration.php:110
msgid "If you're using a custom pull zone, you'll need to use that hostname instead."
msgstr "若您使用自訂 Pull Zone，則需改用該 hostname。"

